cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.PL 

This paper deals with robot motion planning, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The use of temporal logic constraints and probabilistic maps involves artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The optimization problem formulation and heuristic design are related to control systems (cs.SY) and programming languages (cs.PL).
